parameters: "One of the Section Leaders has developed a great interest to one of the children in your Stratum..."
"Proceed with the specimen's delivery to the Hole before next week,\. it's a matter of utmost urgency."
\n<\n[1]>They think they can just take what's mine!?\.\. \BST[3]The "Lady" of this place will taste my claws!
A map of the Hole,\. full of notes and pen marks.
Neneko shakes her,\. the your lady of the mansion groans and whines.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Oh!\.\. You're awake...?\.\. Why are you like this?!
\n<\n[1]>So your maid made a fool out of you?\.\.\. \BST[1,Neneko2]*Shshsh*\.\. Serves you right for what you did to me~
\n<Anzu>You...\.\.\. dealt with that bloodsucker?\.\. ...\.\.\. On my behalf?\.\.
\n<Anzu>My my!\.\. What a precious,\. precious pet I've found myself!\.\. How adorable!
\n<\n[1]>If you hadn't been so haughty to begin with,\. maybe that weakling wouldn't have sucked you dry.\.\. Don't you think,\ blondie?
\n<\n[1]>And you went down twice against the same opponent...\.\.\. \BST[1,Neneko2]is your position just for show?\.\.
\n<Anzu>To think all this potential was hidden in here...\.\.\. just what I needed...
\n<\n[1]>...\.\.\. I'm right here,\. you know?\.\. What about you stop talking to yourself?
\n<Anzu>Hm hm~.\.\. Very well.\.\. Yes,\. stray...\.\.\. we'll talk again soon.
\n<Anzu>You're heading down the Hole,\. right?\.\. In that case,\. I'll be on my way.\.\. One can never be too prepared for that place,\. my kitten.
\n<\n[1]>What's this supposed to mean...?\.\. Will you be there,\. blondie?\.\. ...\.\.\.\BST[3]Hey!
\n<\n[1]>That pervert...\.\.\. I should have left her with the maggot maid...
